author: @Papagamsenjoyer
text: I wasn’t really into K-pop before, but after hearing NewJeans in 2022, they quickly became something special to me. This year has been so hard, and knowing how much the girls have endured makes it even harder to watch. Yet, despite everything, their music and presence have been a comfort to me in ways I can’t explain. I’m grateful I found them, and I can’t imagine not being a fan now. They deserve all the love and more, and I’ll keep supporting them no matter what happens. It hurts to see them go through so much, but I’ll always be here for them 🥲
